<header>
  <h1><img src="https://burger-database-sequelize.herokuapp.com/assets/images/burger.png" alt="burger" id="burger"></h1>
  <h1>EAT-DA-BURGER!</h1>
  <h2><i>Order & Devour Your Favorite Burgers!</i></h2>
  <hr size="6" width="90%" color="red">

  <p>"I was at a restaurant, I saw a guy wearing a leather jacket at the same time he was eating a hamburger and
    drinking a glass of milk. I said, "Dude, you are a cow. The metamorphosis is complete. Don't fall asleep, or I will
    tip you over." ~ Mitch Hedberg</p>
  <hr size="6" width="90%" color="red">

</header>

<div class="toadd col-sm-4" style="max-width: inherit">
  <h5 class="text-center py-1">Place Your Order Here:</h5>
  <div class="form-group">
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="burger_name">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary create-form">Submit</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" style="text-align: -webkit-center; padding-top: 1%">
  <div class="row mb-3" style="justify-content: center">
    <div class="tobedevoured col-sm-5">
      <h5 class="text-center py-1">BURGERS TO BE POUNDED!</h5>
      <ul class="burgers-devoured">
        {{#each burger_data}}
        {{#unless devoured}}
        {{> burgers/burger-block}}
        {{/unless}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="toeat col-sm-4">
      <h5 class="text-center py-1">BURGERS YOU ANNIHALATED!</h5>
      <ul class="burgers-devoured">
        {{#each burger_data}}
        {{#if devoured}}
        {{> burgers/burger-block}}
        {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>